rder 0, not negative):**\n```python\ndef test_order_up_to_ai_no_negative_orders():\n    ai = OrderUpToAI(PlayerRole.RETAILER)\n    state = make_state(inventory=100, backlog=0, pipeline=50)\n    order = ai.decide_order(state)\n    assert order >= 0\n```\n\n**`GameEngine.submit_order` — duplicate submission:**\n```python\ndef test_submit_order_duplicate_raises():\n    engine = GameEngine()\n    state = engine.create_game()\n    state = engine.start_game(state)\n    state = engine.submit_order(state, PlayerRole.RETAILER, 4)\n    with pytest.raises(ValueError):\n        engine.submit_order(state, PlayerRole.RETAILER, 4)\n```\n\n**`GameConfig` — demand pattern shorter than `num_rounds` (wrap):**\n```python\ndef test_demand_pattern_wraps():\n    config = GameConfig(num_rounds=10, demand_pattern=[2, 4])\n    engine = GameEngine()\n    # Round 5 demand should be 2 (pattern[5 % 2])\n    assert engine._get_demand(config, round_idx=5) == 2\n```\n\n---\n\n### Integration Gaps\n\n**Multi-round supply chain propagation:**\n```python\ndef test_demand_propagates_upstream_5_rounds():\n    engine = GameEngine()\n    state = engine.create_game(config=GameConfig(num_rounds=5, demand_pattern=[4]*5))\n    state = engine.start_game(state)\n    for _ in range(5):\n        for role in PlayerRole:\n            state = engine.submit_order(state, role, OrderUpToAI(role).decide_order(state))\n        state = engine.process_round(state)\n    assert state.status == GameStatus.FINISHED\n    assert all(ps.cumulative_cost > 0 for ps in state.players.values())\n```\n\n**Backlog clears before new demand:**\n```python\ndef test_backlog_cleared_before_new_demand():\n    # Setup: retailer has backlog=3, new demand=2, incoming shipment=6\n    # Expected: backlog=0, inventory=1 (6 - 3 - 2)\n    ...\n```\n\n**Cost accumulation is monotonic:**\n```python\ndef test_cumulative_cost_never_decreases():\n    costs = []\n    for round_num in range(game_length):\n        state = engine.process_round(state)\n       